briefdescription.para: Generates the default channel list at runtime, because this is less painful than trying to statically declare it.
This is meant to update the hardware to match the hardware abstraction.

detaileddescription.para: This extracts the hardware mapping of the abstract channel, and then invokes the drivers for the relevant hardware depending on what is mapped in the driver function lookup tables.
